{"tid":1924823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傾緊打唔打功能組別的人同我入晒來！","createTime":"2020-03-14T02:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:16:14.000Z","uid":247494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d3cce07aeb55cd933e112b06990a1892032c72","tid":1924823,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲工會數目幾何級上升，連登仔又做緊咩呢?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1924737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1924737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我知大家各有理據，個個都爭持不下。<br />\n但我想知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">部署、計劃</span></span>係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 支持進攻功能組別<br />\n-成立7人工會<br />\n<br />\n2. 反對進攻功能組別<br />\n-等美國？<br />\n-搞大遊行反對？<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔熟，可能有資料未補充，係呢度講句sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多好多人對個制度存有幻想</span></span>，究竟用道理說服佢地唔信制度，還是儘最大努力證明俾人睇呢？？？<br />\n<br />\n運動都來咗接近9個月，冷卻又有、死去又有，我地係咪要統合資源來做一件事。<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議搵區議員搞個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民大辯論、再以全民投票來決定</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住，我地時間無多。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"c46ea776b0eb0f67b1fb90a75a7b3879590ef34c","tid":1924823,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68b3a22fc1d299fec0933289815489d9eaced04e","tid":1924823,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"成立7人工會懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=65230fde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com/</a>"